rent from other units of government.  UMBAUGH financial consultants are experienced with library projects - from bond issues to property tax projections. We consider it very fulfilling to help libraries through all the financial aspects of completing a project!', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'libraries', '', '', '2011-01-04 16:49:56', '2011-01-04 16:49:56', '', 9, 'http://localhost/umbaugh', 4, 'page', '', 0),
